title: Discover_PTOs_Speak
--- 
<<if $FOHISpeaks == true>>
    //<<pose PTO1BLOOM1>>
    //<<pose PTO2BLOOM1>>
    //<<pose PTO3BLOOM1>>
    <<set $PTOSpeaks = floor(random_range(1, 8))>>
    <<if $PTOSpeaks == 1>>
        Pacific Tree Octopus: It matters what matters we use to think other matters with.
        <<stop>>
        <<endif>>
    <<if $PTOSpeaks == 2>>
        Pacific Tree Octopus: It matters what stories we tell to tell other stories with.
        <<stop>>
        <<endif>>
    <<if $PTOSpeaks == 3>>
        Pacific Tree Octopus: It matters what knots knot knots, what thoughts think thoughts, what descriptions describe descriptions, what ties tie ties.
        <<stop>>
        <<endif>>
    <<if $PTOSpeaks == 4>>
        Pacific Tree Octopus: It matters what stories make worlds, what worlds make stories.
        <<stop>>
        <<endif>>
    <<if $PTOSpeaks == 5>>
        Pacific Tree Octopus: If I entirely change color, shift into a new shape, and completely alter my texture... am I still the same octopus I was before?
        <<endif>>
    <<if $PTOSpeaks == 6>>
        Pacific Tree Octopus: When does the old entity end and the new entity begin?
        <<stop>>
        <<endif>>
    <<if $PTOSpeaks == 7>>
        Pacific Tree Octopus: Man is the only creature who refuses to be what he is.
        <<stop>>
        <<endif>>
    <<if $PTOSpeaks == 8>>
        Pacific Tree Octopus: One must imagine him happy...
        <<stop>>
        <<endif>>
    <<stop>>
<<else>>
    <<stop>>
<<endif>>
